    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Images painted as glazed and fired ceramic tiles that when assembled create a unified depiction of a scene, figures, or panels of unified decorative motifs. These may be fixed to walls or be intended as moveable works, sometimes framed.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
